2ex.com/u/loggerhead", "website": "https://json4u.cn", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "loggerhead", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "takeWhile (not . success) $ repeat try", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47c1/63fd/37749_mini.png?m=1444825425", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47c1/63fd/37749_normal.png?m=1444825425", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47c1/63fd/37749_large.png?m=1444825425", "created": 1366272190, "last_modified": 1444825425}, "last_reply_by": "cat9life", "last_touched": 1727320335, "title": "发布第三天，被最大的竞争对手攻击了，为什么？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1075891", "created": 1727316561, "deleted": 0, "content": "24 号的时候在 [hackernews]( https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=41634356#41647796) 上发帖宣传了一下 [JSON For You]( https://github.com/loggerhead/json4u)。大部分网友讨论的东西都很有启发，帖子热度保持了两天。今天发现 [JSON CRACK]( https://github.com/AykutSarac/jsoncrack.com) 的作者回复我了，结果在进行抹黑：\r\n\r\n```It seems like a clone of https://jsoncrack.com with a different UI. I couldn’t identify any significant differences aside from the reduced readability in the visualization.```\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/006VlDX4gy1hu0vzt4r0gj30z304jmzn.jpg\">\r\n\r\n气得我直接喷了回去，不过也启发了我思考两个问题，想跟大家讨论一下：\r\n\r\n1. 为啥很多商业公司竞争都喜欢去抹黑对手？\r\n2. [JSON For You]( https://json4u.com/) 和 [JSON CRACK]( https://jsoncrack.com/) 体验上各有啥优劣？", "content_rendered": "<p>24 号的时候在 <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=41634356#41647796\" rel=\"nofollow\">hackernews</a> 上发帖宣传了一下 <a href=\"https://github.com/loggerhead/json4u\" rel=\"nofollow\">JSON For You</a>。大部分网友讨论的东西都很有启发，帖子热度保持了两天。今天发现 <a href=\"https://github.com/AykutSarac/jsoncrack.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">JSON CRACK</a> 的作者回复我了，结果在进行抹黑：</p>\n<p><code>It seems like a clone of <a href=\"https://jsoncrack.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://jsoncrack.com</a> with a different UI. I couldn’t identify any significant differences aside from the reduced readability in the visualization.</code></p>\